    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Formally structured organizations, establishments, or associations created for the promotion of a specific benevolent public or private objective, usually a religious, charitable, or educational objective, such as a church, school, college, hospital, asylum, reformatory, mission, or the like.</Note_Text>
